title: Windows XP Professional SP1
description:

             V8429-W6V8V-XP8XK-7734H-Y3396

But remember, use AntiWpa after installing, since the regular activation doesn't work anymore. For me it works best to do it in safe mode, but it probably won't make a difference to you.
